75
00:04:41,708 --> 00:04:42,666
It's bad.

76
00:04:42,750 --> 00:04:44,708
Oh my... Again?

77
00:04:44,791 --> 00:04:46,875
Well that's a side effect
of the medication...

78
00:04:46,958 --> 00:04:48,125
Just try not to
think about it

79
00:04:48,208 --> 00:04:49,750
and it'll go away soon.

80
00:04:51,833 --> 00:04:53,416
I know these symptoms...

81
00:04:53,500 --> 00:04:54,833
I've had them before.

82
00:04:56,750 --> 00:04:58,125
No matter what happens...

83
00:04:58,208 --> 00:05:00,583
I'm ready for
anything that comes...

84
00:05:00,666 --> 00:05:01,625
Because...

85
00:05:01,708 --> 00:05:03,958
