divine punishment.

86
00:05:06,375 --> 00:05:08,083
Hi-ya!

87
00:05:12,000 --> 00:05:13,708
I can't wrap my
head around it,

88
00:05:13,791 --> 00:05:16,666
why is the General
targeting me?

89
00:05:16,750 --> 00:05:18,666
"Those eyes,
whose are they?"...

90
00:05:18,750 --> 00:05:21,125
That's the phrase
I always say.

91
00:05:21,208 --> 00:05:24,125
I even wrote an essay about
it in elementary school...

92
00:05:24,208 --> 00:05:25,958
What exactly did I write?

93
00:05:28,750 --> 00:05:30,583
You lose, you silly boy!

94
00:05:37,041 --> 00:05:38,958
This is it but it
doesn't make any sense.

95
00:05:42,500 --> 00:05:46,750
IR2, huh?

96
00:05:46,833 --> 00:05:48,375
I know this equation,

97
00:05:48,458 --> 00:05:51,041
it's the same one the
General posted online...

98
00:05:51,125 --> 00:05:52,125
Oh no...

99
00:05:52,208 --> 00:05:54,083
What if he's secretly
reading my mind?

100
00:05:58,083 --> 00:05:59,333
The General...

101
00:05:59,416 --> 00:06:00,416
Is it him?

102
00:06:08,708 --> 00:06:09,958
Nanami...

103
00:06:10,041 --> 00:06:11,291
Of course.

104
00:06:11,375 --> 00:06:12,666
Taku.

105
00:06:12,750 --> 00:06:14,375
Yeah, what do you want?

106
00:06:14,458 --> 00:06:16,041
Please... Help me.

107
00:06:17,541 --> 00:06:19,666
Prank-calling me...

108
00:06:19,750 --> 00:06:21,541
She's so annoying.

109
00:06:21,625 --> 00:06:24,250
Yua, have you heard anything
about students at your school

110
00:06:24,333 --> 00:06:27,041
performing magic tricks,
or supernatural feats?

111
