Universe is testing you.

244
00:12:11,333 --> 00:12:13,000
Once you have overcome it,
you will be free again,

245
00:12:13,083 --> 00:12:15,458
and the di- sword
will be summoned.

246
00:12:15,541 --> 00:12:16,541
Trust me...

247
00:12:16,625 --> 00:12:18,583
I know it.

248
00:12:18,666 --> 00:12:20,208
It will appear
before you...

249
00:12:20,291 --> 00:12:22,125
A great black serpent...

250
00:12:22,208 --> 00:12:24,208
It will swallow
up all destruction

251
00:12:24,291 --> 00:12:27,000
and take down the
evil King Gladiale...

252
00:12:27,083 --> 00:12:28,916
This is the
path you are on.

253
00:12:29,000 --> 00:12:30,833
Together we will
destroy the King...

254
00:12:30,916 --> 00:12:32,125
We must.

255
00:12:34,583 --> 00:12:35,708
Well... To be honest,

256
00:12:35,791 --> 00:12:37,333
I have no idea
what's going on...

257
00:12:37,416 --> 00:12:39,250
She's all yours, pal...

258
00:12:39,333 --> 00:12:40,958
Good luck!

259
00:12:41,041 --> 00:12:44,291
Daisuke, leaving me all
alone isn't gonna help.

260
00:12:44,375 --> 00:12:46,791
You created it,
didn't you?

261
00:12:46,875 --> 00:12:48,208
You made the flowerbed.

262
00:12:48,291 --> 00:12:50,750
You gotta understand,
I'm not a gigalomaniac...

263
00:12:50,833 --> 00:12:52,041
I don't think.

